006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.atomic;
007
008import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
009
010public abstract class AbstractDateTimeItem<TYPE>
011    extends AbstractTemporalItem<TYPE>
012    implements IDateTimeItem {
013  /**
014   * Construct a new item with the provided {@code value}.
015   *
016   * @param value
017   *          the value to wrap
018   */
019  protected AbstractDateTimeItem(@NonNull TYPE value) {
020    super(value);
021  }
022
023  @Override
024  public boolean hasTimezone() {
025    return true;
026  }
027
028  @Override
029  public int hashCode() {
030    return asZonedDateTime().hashCode();
031  }
032
033  @SuppressWarnings("PMD.OnlyOneReturn")
034  @Override
035  public boolean equals(Object obj) {
036    return this == obj
037        || (obj instanceof IDateTimeItem && compareTo((IDateTimeItem) obj) == 0);
038  }
039}
